Install project dependencies:
npm install

Start a Base Sepolia fork in another terminal:
export NODE_NO_WARNINGS=1
INFURA_KEY=${INFURA_API_KEY}
npx hardhat node --fork https://base-sepolia.infura.io/v3/$INFURA_KEY --chain-id 84532

The forked node listens on http://127.0.0.1:8545 with 20 funded accounts.

Deploy contracts to the fork (optional):
npx hardhat deploy --network development

This runs the deploy scripts in deploy/ in order:
01_aggregator.js → 02_keeper.js → 03_config.js

Run the test suite against the fork:
export NODE_NO_WARNINGS=1
npx hardhat test --network development

Run the test scripts:
./test.sh
